original_title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy! Escape from Dino Island
overview: Escape From Dino Island is a Wow! Wow! Wubbzy! DVD that contains two episodes from Season 1 and five episodes from Season 2 (six including one bonus episode). This DVD largely focuses on episodes about Dino Island, wild jungles, and planting.
title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy! Escape from Dino Island
